Sketch : d_TilingSystem_01

--------------------------------

This sketch demonstrates how we can
create a different kind of grid system using FOR loops
& a few calculations. It has perhaps more flexibility 
for developments

- MOUSE changes stroke thickness
- KEYS 1, 2, 3 change the stroke settings
- KEYS 5, 6 change the tiling system
- KEY 'r' generates a new composition
- KEYS 'a' & 'z' increase/decrease line length
- KEYS 'UP' & 'DOWN' increase/decrease number of rows
- KEYS 'RIGHT' & 'LEFT' increase/decrease number of columns   
- KEYS 'm' & 'k' / 'o' & 'l' increase/decrease grid resolution


